version_description:
Enjoy our new search spotlights and filters to help you find and save the best leads. Try notes and tags on accounts and leads to stay organized and remember key moments.
Search Spotlights: Job Changes, TeamLink Introductions, Mentioned in the News, Recent Posts, Shared Experiences, & Follow Your Company
Search Filters: Geography, Relationship, Current Company, Industry, Company Size, Current Title, & Seniority Level.

Enjoy our new messaging experience
- Stay organized with threaded messages
- Mention icebreakers to improve response rate
- Easily send messages 
- Send image attachments
- View pdfs, word docs, images and other attachments
- Bug Fixes
Bug Fixes
Bug Fixes

Prepare to tackle the day with Mobile Daily Briefings, delivering important updates about your upcoming meetings to the palm of your hand.

Build rapport with attendees
• Know who's attending your meeting, understand their role in the organization, and uncover meaningful icebreakers

Be prepared
• Review relevant and recent information about attendee's company prior to meetings

Stay up-to-date
• Receive actionable updates on your saved leads and accounts, including job changes and when leads actions
Bug fixes and feature enhancements
